  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Luid ta Debbes preeza-\njahs/ un ta Semine lihgimo-\njahs/ un lai fakka starp teem Pa-\nganeem/ tas KUNGS irr Keh-\nnisch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid ta Juhra kanz/ un\nwiſſ/ kas eekſch tahs irr/ lai\nLauki lihgimojahs ar wiſſu/ kas\nwinnu Wirſu irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad gawilehs tee Mescha\nKohki ta KUNGA Preekchá/ jo\ntas nahk to Semni teefahrt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tetzeet to KUNGU/ jo\nwinch irr labs/ jo winna Scheh-\nlastiba paleeſ muhſchigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fakkait: Atpesti muhs\nDeews muhfas Bestifchanas/ un\nfapulze muhs/ un iglahb muhs\nno teem Paganeem/ ka mehs ta-\nwu fivehtu Wahrdtu teizam/ un\ntew augsti flawejam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Slawehts lat irr tas\nKUNGS Israëta Deews muh-\nschigi muhſcham/ ua lat wiſſi widē atgreeſahs jawu Naimmu\nLandis fakka: Amen/ un to fivehtiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta painette winch tur\npreekſch ta KUNGA Derribás\nSchkirstu Affawn/ un winna\nBrahtus weenumehr ta Schkir-\nsta Preekchá kalpoht/ ikdeenas\nfawa Rahrtá.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Obed-Eedoms ar fa-\nweein Brahteem bija fechdesmits\nun astoni/ (un winch eezehle)\nObed-Eedomu Jedituxa Dehtu/\nun Offu par Wahrtu-Sargeem/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Preesteri Zadaku/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "un winna Brahtus par Pree-\nstereem preekſch ta KUNGA\nDshwokli us to Augstumu/ kas\nGibeoná bija/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam KUNSAM De-\ndsamu-Uppurus uppureht us to\nDedsamu-Uppuru Altari weenn-\nmehr/Rihtōs un Wakkards/pehz\nwiſſu/ kas rakſtihts ta KUNGA\nBauslibá/ ko winch Israëtam\nbij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ar winneem Eemans\nun Jedituns/ un tee zitti Jsweh-\nleti/ kas pee Wahrdeem nofaukti\ntappe to KUNGU teikt/ jo win-\nna Schehlastiba paleeſ muh-\nschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ar teem Eemans un\nJedituns ar Trummnetehm un\nPulkstenifscheem skandinaht/ un\nar Deewa Dseefinu Rihtkeem/\nbet Jedituna Behrni tappe par\nWahrtu-Sargeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta nogahje wiſſi Laudis\nikkats jawā Naimnā/ ir Dah-\nwids widē atgreeſahs jawu Naimmu\n"
    }
  ],
